Our new <span style="color: #c00000;">**VSPD**</span> is signed into existance. Everyone knows it is more a continuation of the <span style="color: #c00000;">**MSPD**</span> than the <span style="color: #D47B9B;">**USPD**</span> but most can settle themselves with the state of things as they are.

Many <span style="color: #D47B9B;">**USPD**</span> members are reluctant to join but see no other alternatives. Many join the <span style="color: #700000;">**KPD**</span> instead with only a tiny rest remaining in the "Rest-<span style="color: #D47B9B;">**USPD**</span>".

The promise of adopting a new programm eventually helps a lot with reconciliation, though we have yet to see how our bourgeois allies will react to that.

