Many <span style="color: #D47B9B;">**USPD**</span> members are reluctant to join but see no other alternatives. Many join the <span style="color: #700000;">**KPD**</span> instead with only a tiny rest remaining in the "Rest-<span style="color: #D47B9B;">**USPD**</span>".

